Lynch famously found stocks by observing the real world:

```python
def lynch_walk_around_ideas():
    """
    Peter Lynch's famous "walk around" method
    
    Find investment ideas in everyday life
    """
    
    categories_to_watch = {
        'Shopping Mall': [
            "Which stores have longest lines?",
